      <p class="mb-60">At the very core of our coffee journey lies 'Esencia de Cafe,' a cherished treasure steeped in history and tradition. Translating to "Essence of Coffee," this revered elixir traces its roots back through the annals of time, connecting us to the heart of El Salvador's coffee heritage.</p>
      <div class="flex-image-first">
